00:00:00,800 --> 00:00:08,440
In this American English pronunciation video, we're going to learn how to pronounce the schwa vowel sound.
在这段美式英语发音视频中，我们将学习如何发音中元音音素。

2
00:00:15,200 --> 00:00:18,680
This vowel is always unstressed.
这个元音总是非重读的。

3
00:00:19,720 --> 00:00:29,240
The mouth position is a lot like the UH as in BUTTER vowel, but that vowel can be, and usually is, stressed.
嘴巴的位置很像 BUTTER 中的 UH 元音，但那个元音可以是重读的，通常也是重读的。

4
00:00:30,520 --> 00:00:37,340
But just like that vowel, everything in your lips, jaw, and neck should be relaxed for this sound.
但就像那个元音一样，你的嘴唇、下巴和脖子的一切都应该放松来发出这个音。

5
00:00:38,528 --> 00:00:41,480
Just slightly drop your jaw to make this sound.
只需稍微放下下巴来发出这个音。

6
00:00:42,160 --> 00:00:44,700
The trick is to keep everything else relaxed.
诀窍是保持其他一切放松。

7
00:00:46,368 --> 00:00:49,440
Let's look at the vowel up close and in slow motion.
让我们近距离慢动作观察这个元音。

8
00:00:50,368 --> 00:01:02,500
It's possible to make this sound on its own with just the slightest jaw drop, but in actual words, you will likely see a bit more jaw drop, like here on the word SOFA.
可以仅通过轻微的下巴下垂来单独发出这个音，但在实际单词中，你可能会看到下巴下垂得更多，比如在单词 SOFA 中。

9
00:01:03,712 --> 00:01:09,000
Lips relaxed, cheeks relaxed, tongue forward and relaxed.
嘴唇放松，脸颊放松，舌头向前并放松。

10
00:01:10,520 --> 00:01:14,780
As I said, this vowel can only be in an unstressed syllable.
正如我所说，这个元音只能出现在非重读音节中。

11
00:01:15,880 --> 00:01:21,220
All other vowel and diphthong sounds can either be stressed or unstressed.
所有其他元音和双元音音素可以是重读或非重读的。

12
00:01:22,420 --> 00:01:26,660
So the schwa will always be really fast and low in pitch.
所以中元音总是非常快且音调低。

